    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Gilding only the top edges of books after they have been cut smooth, leaving the other edges ungilded and trimmed or uncut.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
